     C****                 ENDIF
      *今回/前回
     C                     Z-ADD0         RITU    72
     C           SVKMAX    IFNE 0
     C           WMAIS     DIV  SVKMAX    RITU
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MULT 100       RITU
